snippet.title: The Sims 4 Get to Work: Official Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore new active careers in The Sims 4 Get to Work Expansion Pack, available April 2015.

Learn more: http://o.ea.com/34325 

Save lives, solve crimes, create inventions, build a retail business and more in the first expansion pack for The Sims 4.

#sims4 #gettowork
